<br />
Weapons (2)<br />
Darth Vader&#39;s Lightsaber (V) x2<br />
<br />
Objective (1)<br />
Hunt Down And Destroy The Jedi / Their Fire Has Gone Out Of The Universe<br />
<br />
The basic premise of this deck is to use Expand The Empire on the Holotheater to get +6 activation, and then use Vader on the ground with his new lightsaber to own anyone who comes at him.  With the lightsaber and Vader&#39;s choking ability already helping hold a site, cards like Put All Sections On Alert, Sniper, I Have You Now, and You Are Beaten, Vader is very close to a one-man army.  The space is enough to do hit-and-runs or to satisfy Battle Order in the late game, and the very high destiny of the deck makes sure that Vader will always hit or choke what he&#39;s aiming for, and Counter Assault is capable of doing some game-ending damage.<br />
<br />
Try out Darth Vader&#39;s Lightsaber (V) and you will see how much more powerful Vader can become.  Armed with this new weapon, he will truly be able to hunt down and destroy all of the Jedi.<br />
